                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def2-1673-18430508 t18430508-1673-punishment-243"></join>Transported for Ten years</rs>.</hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Before Mr. Common Sergeant.</hi>
